              "help": {
                "text": "Vulnerability GHSA-mh29-5h37-fv8m\nSeverity: medium\nPackage: js-yaml\nVersion: 3.14.1\nFix Version: 3.14.2\nType: npm\nLocation: /tavus-pipecat-example/frontend/package-lock.json\nData Namespace: github:language:javascript\nLink: [GHSA-mh29-5h37-fv8m](https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-mh29-5h37-fv8m)",
                "markdown": "**Vulnerability GHSA-mh29-5h37-fv8m**\n| Severity | Package | Version | Fix Version | Type | Location | Data Namespace | Link |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| medium  | js-yaml  | 3.14.1  | 3.14.2  | npm  | /tavus-pipecat-example/frontend/package-lock.json  | github:language:javascript  | [GHSA-mh29-5h37-fv8m](https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-mh29-5h37-fv8m)  |\n"
